snippet.title: We Took That Trip (Lucito Loquito) // The Mini Indie Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Embark on a relaxing road trip with your closest friends. Maintain your beloved van, deal with its innovative systems, and give it a personal touch by customizing it. Enjoy the journey and discover the emotional story of your group of friends.

Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1754250/We_Took_That_Trip/

The Mini Indie Showcase 2023: https://youtu.be/ANsVkLxB3e0 

Learn more: https://sixoneindie.com/showcase
